spisnif component
========================


FPGA component
--------------

spisnif is composed of xxx 16 bits register :

|   offset   | name           | description                 |
|:-----------|:--------------:|:---------------------------:|
|    0x00    | CONTROL        | Control register            |

+ **CONTROL** : Control register

| 15 downto 4 |  3   |        2     |           1       |   0   |
|:-----------:|:----:|:------------:|:-----------------:|:-----:|
|    void     | busy | start/stop_n | RAM pointer reset | Reset |


ARMadeus linux driver
---------------------

